overview: Buckle your safety restraints and keep all appendages inside the vehicle, you're in for a wild roller coaster ride with the Baby Jesus of Bristish Wrestling, Rockstar Spud.  Rob Naylor is back with a man of equal stature and these two shoot on anything and everything from breaking in the business in the UK to Crazy Steve's glorious hog. Seriously, folks. This interview is fun and outrageous and most importantly entertaining.
title: Hitting The Highspots - Rockstar Spud
